INSTALL

Installation is very simple.

1) Download package from http://www.quincecontroller.org/download.html
2) Extract into web accessible directory
3) That should be all


POSSIBLE PROBLEMS:
1) Make sure that the directory you've installed package is writable by webserver
2) If yo're using templates, make sure that Libraries/Smarty/templates_c is writeable
3) Check that your server allows htaccess to override settings with htaccess file

DocumentRoot "/path/to/web"

<Directory />
    Options FollowSymLinks All
    AllowOverride All
</Directory>





